      "score": 38,
      "comments": 19,
      "author": "confusedalex",
      "published": "2026-07-03T23:23:43Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Minimize homelab toil by adopting GitOps tools like ArgoCD or Flux to automatically sync state from Git repositories.",
        "Use declarative operating systems like NixOS or IaC tools like Terraform to enable reproducible, self-healing, zero-maintenance infrastructure.",
        "Implement automated dependency and container updates via Renovate or Watchtower to eliminate manual patching and version drift."
      ]
    },
